   Completely filling your view screen, you see before you the    Crimson bloated substance of an ancient red dwarf star.   It projects an apparent malevolence which chills you to your   Innermost core.   Nothing in your experience could ever quite prepare   You for your first visualization of the Star.....MALIGNA.   This then is the rogue star which astronomers predicted would in time   Travel into the Milky Way Galaxy disturbing the stellar order   With its oscillating gravitational field.   You must destroy this anomalous astral demon before it begins   Its terrible journey and wreaks havoc upon your galaxy.   If you've had the foresight to come equipped with the   Star-Buster Seige Weapon then your mission can be easily    Accomplished while the Archangel Shield System protects you and   Your ship from the horrendous and deadly full spectrum   Radiation that is emanating from the old star.   Remember the Directive to save the Galaxy and vigorously use your   Ship and its armament for the good of all.